beer.beer_description:
Bright & zingy. Real fruit. Soft mouthfeel.

Someday Sour Beers are fabulously refreshing beers with real fruit flavours bursting through. Super easy on the palate with a soft body and very low bitterness.

Someday shines with bright and zingy acidity, balanced with soft and pillowy pale and wheat malts. 

The Blood Orange bursts onto the centre stage, delivering layers of flavour and refreshment.

Make Someday Today!

items.badge_description: Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 30 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 7! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

Its been a long day and now its time for a reward. Crisp, tasty and refreshing, enjoy that delicious fruit beer! That's 30 different beers with the style of Fruit Beer, Sour - Smoothie / Pastry, or Sour - Fruited (Gose or Berliner Weisse). Try 5 more for Level 7!

items.checkin_comment: Smells great, subtle but great flavour

items.badge_description: Beer is often better with friends. Besides, drinking socially is what we're all about! You've checked in with at least 10 other people within 5 hours.
Drinking with friends is fun. Right? You've checked in with at least 4 other people within 2 hours.
So, you're new around here? Congrats on your first brew! This one's for you.

Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!
